node.text:
We had the best time this weekend at the #NYTFoodFestival eating incredible food from @leonellinyc @morgansternsnyc @marcforgione and more!
The @nytimes & @nytlive brought together some of NYC’s best restaurants and vendors for two special days of food in Bryant Park and we already can’t wait until next year 😝
#newforkcity

Photo shared by New Fork City on July 28, 2021 tagging @jokrnyc. May be an image of dessert.

node.text:
The Summer of snacking is here! Using @jokrnyc we were able to order all these goodies for our snack board, with delivery in under 15 minutes! They carry some of our NY favorites like the @milkbarstore compost cookies and @levainbakery two chip cookies. You can order on Jokr using our code NYC25OFF for $25 OFF on each of your first two orders and you’ll get FREE @mahzedahrbakery peanut brittle with your order. Now that’s a snack plate worth celebrating… #ad
#newforkcity
